# Render image build context = repo root, but only services/render +
# deps/cadgamefusion are needed, plus the shared diff engine the image COPYs
# (tools/render_regression/{diff,compare}.py — POST /diff reuses it). Exclude
# everything else, then re-include those, then drop heavy nested build/cache
# dirs and the regression dir's non-engine parts (golden DXFs, corpus
# manifests with customer filenames, tests) so only the two .py files ship.
*
!services/render
!deps/cadgamefusion
!tools/render_regression
tools/render_regression/golden/
tools/render_regression/tests/
tools/render_regression/*_manifest_*.json
tools/render_regression/baselines*.json
**/.git
**/build/
**/build_*/
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/vcpkg_installed
**/node_modules
